Creating Base.dll:
------------------

cd stockhausen
sml @SMLload=stoc/stoc-com+ lib/bootstrap/Bootstrap.aus vm-com+/Base.il
ilasm /dll vm-com+/Base.il


Building a Distribution:
------------------------

export STOCKHOME=~/stockhausen/vm-com+

stockhausen/bin/stoc.bat (TBD)
stockhausen/bin/stow.exe (former Start.exe)
stockhausen/stoc-com+.x86-win32
stockhausen/Default.import (absolute path inside)
stockhausen/lib/Base.dll
stockhausen/lib/TextIO.dll (from TextIO.aml)
stockhausen/lib/CommandLine.dll (TBD)
stockhausen/lib/IO.dll (TBD)
stockhausen/lib/OS.dll (TBD)
stockhausen/lib/TextIO.dll (TBD)
